name: Security Camera Domed
description:
Simulated Security Cameras are a Proven Crime Deterrent.  Only you know it's fake.
32SC2014 Non Functioning Security Camera features silver metal like finish, blinking red light and 19 faux clear LED bulbs. Requires 2 AAA batteries (not included). Measures 2 5/8" x 6" x 5 1/2".

32SC2013 Non Functioning Domed Security Camera features a motion detecting sensor that makes it appear to work as an actual security camera! A light will come on when the sensor is activated. No wiring needed. Requires 2 AA batteries (not included). Measures 4 5/8" x 3" x 4 5/8".

32SC2016 Large Non Functioning Domed Security Camera  features a motion detecting sensor that makes it appear to work as an actual security camera! A light will come on when the sensor is activated. No wiring needed. Requires 2 AA batteries (not included).
Measures 8 1/4" x 5-1/4" x 8 1/4".

name: T-O-M Tickets White 1 ROLL=3M
description:
Turn-O-Matic Tickets for use with your Turn-O-Matic system.
All Turn-O-Matic Tickets are sold by the package
T80 Tickets Item #3300 & 3300A-Alpha -5 rolls per package (3,000 tickets per roll), total of 15,000 tickets per package.
T90 Tickets Item #33008 -6 rolls per package (4,000 tickets per roll), total of 24,000 tickets per package.
